.TH TerminalLister 3 "Last change: 29 May 2000" "Release 0.5" "Ulm's Oberon System"
.SH NAME
TerminalLister \- listing generation on base of \fITerminals(3)\fP
.SH SYNOPSIS
.Pg
PROCEDURE Init(s: Streams.Stream) : BOOLEAN;
.Pe
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I TerminalLister
provides an implementation for \fIListers(3)\fP that is based
upon \fITerminals(3)\fP and \fITermAttributes(3)\fP.
.LP
.I Init
installs the interface procedures of \fIListers(3)\fP for \fIs\fP
that must support the operations of \fITerminals(3)\fP and
\fITermAttributes(3)\fP. Following attributes are tested in
the given order whether they are supported by the terminal device
associated with \fIs\fP: \fIstandout\fP, \fIreverse\fP,
\fIunderline\fP, \fIdim\fP, \fIbold\fP, and \fIblink\fP.
If none of these attributes are supported and/or the number
of columns appears to small, \fBFALSE\fP is returned.
.SH DIAGNOSTICS
.I TerminalLister
does not generate any error events on its own.
.I Init
and all interface procedures of \fIListers(3)\fP return \fBFALSE\fP
in case of errors.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.Tb CompilerErrors(3)
